description:
Ideally located minutes from Epping Station/Town Centre, local shops, café/dining, parks & more

Terrace-style Home in boutique building on quiet street
Occupying 102sqm: apartment 86sqm, carspace 14sqm & lock-up storage 2sqm
Perfect indoor & outdoor living in leafy surrounds
Open plan lounge and dining, finished in neutral tones
Extra high floor-to-ceiling glass; East facing outlook
Abundant natural light; easy care timber floors
Private garden courtyard ideal for relaxation or entertaining
Separate, window area suits a study or home office
Gourmet kitchen, Caesar Stone top, Miele appliances
Ducted Air Con, Dishwasher, Dryer, Internal Laundry.
Security carspace
Separate lock-up storage
Low levies

Pet friendly

Easy access to M2 Highway, national parks, shopping centres, schools & Uni.
